OL,5, For 28-year-old geography teacher      
OL,6, Kamran Manafly, it all began with an   
OL,7, Instagram post.                        
OL,9,F"I don't want to be a reflection of    
OL,10,Fstate propaganda," he wrote on the     
OL,11,Fsocial media site, just a few days     
OL,12,Fbefore it was restricted in Russia. "I 
OL,13,Fhave my own opinion! Lots of teachers  
OL,14,Fdo. And you know what? It's not the    
OL,15,Fsame as the opinion of the state."     
OL,18,FTwo hours after posting, he received a 
OL,19,Fcall from the school's headteacher     
OL,20,Ftelling him to delete it immediately,  
OL,21,For leave his job.                      
